# SimpleOS Kernel — MDSOC Architecture
#
# Organized by MDSOC dimensions:
#
# ENTITY dimension (types/):
#   types/   — Core OS types (VmMap, TaskContext, CapabilityToken, etc.)
#   arch/    — Architecture-specific types (x86, RISC-V, ARM)
#
# FEATURE dimension (directional layers, boot → memory → ... → ipc):
#   boot/        — Limine entry, early serial, boot info (Layer 0)
#   memory/      — PMM, VMM, paging, kernel heap (Layer 1)
#   interrupts/  — IDT/GDT, APIC, exception handlers (Layer 2)
#   scheduler/   — Preemptive scheduler, task management (Layer 3)
#   ipc/         — Message passing, capability system, pledge/unveil (Layer 4)
#
# TRANSFORM dimension (adapters):
#   arch_adapt/  — Platform-specific → generic kernel port bridges
#
# Layering enforced at compile time via capsule.sdn.
# Upper layers may depend on lower layers, never reverse.
